Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.21,0:00:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everyone, Kaleido Star is about to start.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.18,0:00:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When you watch Kaleido Star,\Nplease keep your room bright,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.93,0:00:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and sit as far from the TV as you can.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.76,0:00:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, well, well. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.29,0:00:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Have you ever had times when you\Ndidn't know what you wanted to do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.17,0:00:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's exactly the way I am right now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.13,0:00:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I worked hard, trying to \Nget into Kaleido Stage.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.43,0:00:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then I worked hard so that I'd\Nbe acknowledged by everyone,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.47,0:00:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and I worked hard trying\Nto catch up with Miss Layla.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.02,0:00:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But, I wonder what I'm working hard for now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.14,0:00:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No... Not good. Not good.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.73,0:00:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't become a star with my\Nfeelings all wishy-washy like this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.68,0:00:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't! I can't!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.92,0:01:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tattoo Kiss hajimari wa \Naka to kuro no Passion{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.25,0:01:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Toki ni urahara na kokoro o tayori ni{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.57,0:01:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tattoo Kiss kirifuda wa mirai o kaeru Mission{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.82,0:01:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Koi ni aimai na kotae wa iranai {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.89,0:01:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Arienai genjitsu minai furi shite mo Bet{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.24,0:01:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Egatai shinjitsu\NCan U feel me now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.20,0:01:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nesshiyasui jibun ni Say What? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.56,0:01:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tomadou iibun {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.62,0:01:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dreamin' samenai yume ochiteku sadame{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.17,0:02:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't stop lovin' can't stop lovin' you\NYa ya ya{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.51,0:02:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Believe in U hikikae ni subete ushinatte mo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.36,0:02:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Still lovin' can't stop lovin' you\NNo no no{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.16,0:02:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tattoo Kiss {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.35,0:02:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.90,0:02:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is my duel with fate! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.27,0:02:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Demon Spiral!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.30,0:02:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her movements are too irregular;\Nit's impossible to follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.81,0:02:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing... Can he grab her?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.19,0:02:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not good. She doesn't have enough height.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.37,0:03:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A devil's maneuver?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.71,0:03:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That certainly might be\Nappropriate for a partner of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.51,0:03:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.39,0:03:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems this has been decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.96,0:03:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Amazing Angelic Counterattack."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.38,0:03:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even for someone like Sora,\Nit must be quite a shock this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.21,0:03:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even say anything to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.95,0:03:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's leave her alone right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.06,0:03:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.04,0:04:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Demon Spiral... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.92,0:04:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}May had a shoulder injury, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.15,0:04:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but she used that to invent a new maneuver.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.18,0:04:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And she got the Phoenix Ticket. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.57,0:04:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.32,0:04:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.98,0:04:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.76,0:04:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To tell you the truth, I didn't\Nthink May would go that far either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.66,0:04:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was actually moved by the fact\Nthat she invented a new maneuver
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.41,0:04:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by taking advantage of her injuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.66,0:04:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.07,0:04:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.67,0:04:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,before Yuri and I participated \Nin the Circus Festival,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.42,0:04:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kalos told us this:
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.09,0:04:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen very carefully, both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.79,0:04:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you cannot win, don't come back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.37,0:04:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you cannot win in the Circus Festival,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.44,0:04:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you two have nowhere to come back to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.78,0:05:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Boss told you something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.43,0:05:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was why I didn't\Nhave any choice but to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.93,0:05:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you won your duel with fate.\NYou really are amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.59,0:05:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.27,0:05:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will try to improve my skills
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.41,0:05:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so that I can keep up with May.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.14,0:05:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, are you thinking you lost to May
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.10,0:05:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because you didn't have enough skills?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.56,0:05:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.51,0:05:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I thought you didn't have enough skills,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.57,0:05:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never would have recommended you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.99,0:05:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You lost because the festival meant\Nonly that much to you. Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.48,0:05:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I never thought that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.78,0:05:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To me, it was something I needed\Nto enter and win by all means.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.05,0:05:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To me, it was worth that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.88,0:05:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, for you, it was not worth that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.30,0:05:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, I will ask you one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.26,0:06:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you seriously want to participate in\Nthe Circus Festival no matter what happens?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.02,0:06:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.32,0:06:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you make up your mind and decide
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.14,0:06:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to seriously follow through, \Nyou never give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.20,0:06:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that better than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.29,0:06:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But here you are, right now,\Nhaving given up on everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.10,0:06:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's proof that you \Nweren't serious about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.45,0:06:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I told you after the Salome show.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.44,0:06:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't feel enough of that edge\Nfrom you right now to be scared of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.37,0:06:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've lost track of what's important.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.11,0:06:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted you to enter to the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.24,0:06:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.94,0:07:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe what I did...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.08,0:07:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.32,0:07:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I betrayed Miss Layla's expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.62,0:07:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, Sora, take the tape off!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.87,0:07:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to do something. \NI have to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.27,0:07:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What can I do? Tell me, Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.01,0:07:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know the answer either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.73,0:07:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're no help.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.42,0:07:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you supposed to be on my side?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.62,0:07:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you give me some\Nclever advice or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.54,0:07:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the spirit of the stage.\NI'm neither enemy nor ally.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.57,0:07:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One more time, I want \Nto have one more chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.24,0:07:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I can't believe\NI feel this way at this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.15,0:07:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.62,0:07:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing I can tell you is this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.28,0:07:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The deadline for Circus Festival\Nentries hasn't passed yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.86,0:08:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sagittarius is still not able to\Nfind its way out from the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.34,0:08:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, nearby Sagittarius,\NI can see another arrow;
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.67,0:08:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,an arrow shining, as if it's guiding\Nher way out from the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.88,0:08:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another arrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.11,0:08:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Phoenix Tickets are the "seed" right\Nwhich were given to those two who won.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.42,0:08:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.31,0:08:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.82,0:08:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's one more ticket!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.50,0:08:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is! There is! There is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.49,0:08:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--There's another ticket!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.37,0:08:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I can't breathe! I'm gonna wee!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.60,0:08:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri is studying in Paris \Nright now, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.46,0:08:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Circus Festival will be\Nheld in Paris too. It's perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.08,0:08:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take me to Paris, quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.97,0:08:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Paris?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.85,0:08:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri hasn't even registered for the festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.11,0:08:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He might not have any \Nintention of being in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.81,0:08:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First of all, it's impossible\Nto go to Paris by cab.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.29,0:08:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible or not,\Nthere's nothing to do but ask!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.06,0:09:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I realized that I can't just keep\Nmoping about how I lost to May.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.51,0:09:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just have to acknowledge\Nmy defeat and do what I can now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.42,0:09:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll end up being absent from Kids' \NStage, but Marion's accepted it,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.84,0:09:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so things should be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.86,0:09:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think Sora's \Nback to her usual self?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.40,0:09:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's true, we can't stop her now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.34,0:09:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.95,0:09:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosetta!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.44,0:09:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the guide book for Paris\Nwhich I used to use a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.58,0:09:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's some French phrases\Ntoo, although it's not much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.63,0:09:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. This will help.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.17,0:09:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, a winter coat. It's cold over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.30,0:09:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosetta, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.18,0:09:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.27,0:09:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.70,0:09:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Paris... It must be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.08,0:09:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The clown I admire, Mr. Charlie, is there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.83,0:09:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! So Anna, you're rarin' to go too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.25,0:09:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you put it like \Nthat, I'm{\i1} parin{\i0}' to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.06,0:10:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Je... Je...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.21,0:10:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Je t'aime. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.12,0:10:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.97,0:10:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The God of Death, Leon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.30,0:10:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The God of Death's come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.58,0:10:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll finish checking in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.99,0:10:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.80,0:10:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leon, I've not seen you for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.17,0:10:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Emma...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.27,0:10:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you remember me? I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.35,0:10:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you his new partner?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.12,0:10:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I am Leon's partner, May Wong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.95,0:10:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Poor you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.93,0:10:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once the Circus Festival is\Nover, you'll be discarded too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.84,0:10:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Just who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.81,0:11:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, please don't put us\Non the same floor as Leon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.14,0:11:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll make my performers nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.98,0:11:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't arrange \Nthis, I'll change hotels!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.83,0:11:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait for a moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.36,0:11:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a message for\NMr. Ken Robbins from Kaleido Stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.03,0:11:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? For me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.91,0:11:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I will create a chance for you to show off."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.24,0:11:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, did you hear it too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.09,0:11:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The whisper of the God of Death?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.57,0:11:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will create a perfect chance\Nfor you to show off in today's show.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.35,0:11:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The whisper of the God of Death"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.02,0:11:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you also Leon's partner?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.90,0:11:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Partner? Nobody can be Leon's partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.09,0:11:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody but her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.38,0:11:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.72,0:11:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora's in Paris?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.15,0:11:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Er... The drama school where Yuri is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.74,0:12:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't read French!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.96,0:12:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where? Where? Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.52,0:12:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.56,0:12:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. I'll try to look for her too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.33,0:12:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.42,0:12:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, okay, but... where should I look?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Er... {\i1}Me-Merci.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.65,0:12:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My money's all gone after\NI took the cab. Well, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.55,0:12:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.90,0:12:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Non{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.24,0:12:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? He is not here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.32,0:12:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mais, c'est bien ici le... Conservatoire...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.94,0:12:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.83,0:12:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what shall I do...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.42,0:12:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're looking for Yuri,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.03,0:12:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he wasn't in class today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.38,0:12:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.34,0:13:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, he is here, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.50,0:13:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.84,0:13:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.84,0:13:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, but do you know where Yuri is now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.34,0:13:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's, how should I put it,\Nhe marches to his own beat,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.75,0:13:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or shall I say, he's difficult to approach...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.55,0:13:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But anyway, I don't really know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.30,0:13:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you know where he lives either?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.90,0:13:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.98,0:13:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.13,0:13:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.40,0:13:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, there is no clue. What shall I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.71,0:13:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Circus Festival...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.45,0:13:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure... I'm sure Yuri will\Ncome here too. I'm sure! I'm sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.78,0:13:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... So, this is the hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.51,0:13:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, they're performing! Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.26,0:13:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Merci, merci. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.79,0:13:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know! If I make some money here,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.39,0:13:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can look for Yuri, and I can eat something!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.54,0:14:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not at a dead end yet. I'm not! I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.54,0:14:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, they're getting fired up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.79,0:14:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Mute and Alice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.27,0:14:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is something of a performer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.41,0:14:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's amazing. But I've \Nnever seen her before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.75,0:14:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's pretty good. Who is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.65,0:14:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.22,0:14:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.36,0:14:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Super!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.62,0:14:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Brava{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.46,0:14:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... {\i1}Merci{\i0}! {\i1}Merci{\i0}! {\i1}Merci{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.52,0:14:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, now I can eat something with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.60,0:14:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.96,0:14:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hurt yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.87,0:14:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... I understand what \Nhe is saying. I'm lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.17,0:14:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What did you say? Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.40,0:15:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really... I thought you\Nhurt yourself. I was worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.32,0:15:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoever would have\Nthought she was just hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.24,0:15:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! I haven't eaten\Nanything since I got to Paris, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.77,0:15:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's impressive that you\Ncan manage maneuvers like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.92,0:15:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to enter the Circus\NFestival no matter what, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.56,0:15:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to participate in the festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.32,0:15:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.65,0:15:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mute and Alice, you too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.65,0:15:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.60,0:15:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We want to win in the festival\Nand get the world's attention,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.37,0:15:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and organize a performance team with\Nthese guys right here, and travel around.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.05,0:15:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is our dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.70,0:15:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's dreams rest\Nheavily on Mute's shoulders.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.44,0:15:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.40,0:15:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.55,0:15:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you also come here to\Nmake your dream come true, Sora?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.39,0:16:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give up that dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.67,0:16:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An angel always keeps\Nan eye on us somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.87,0:16:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An angel...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.58,0:16:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My angel...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.18,0:16:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.14,0:16:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.50,0:16:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.83,0:16:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you know, it's Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.40,0:16:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.61,0:16:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri... Don't tell me he's {\i1}the {\i0}Yuri Killian.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.60,0:16:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does she know Yuri Killian\Nwho won the last time?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.31,0:16:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who on Earth is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.49,0:16:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.10,0:16:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm glad. I finally found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.73,0:16:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was sure you would come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.44,0:16:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoever thought I would\Nsee you in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.01,0:16:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a long time, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.59,0:16:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.35,0:16:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An angel always keeps an eye on you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.10,0:16:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Miss Layla, I will never give up on\Nparticipating in this Circus Festival.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.69,0:17:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... It's such a different\Natmosphere from America or Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.09,0:17:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's calm, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.88,0:17:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.43,0:17:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like you've\Ncompletely adjusted to Paris.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.66,0:17:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.69,0:17:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.55,0:17:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... To tell you the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.56,0:17:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came to Paris because\NI wanted to ask you a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.36,0:17:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A favor? What kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.20,0:17:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have Phoenix Tickets, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.33,0:17:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I do. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.24,0:17:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using those tickets,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.10,0:17:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to participate in\Nthe Circus Festival with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.94,0:17:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is a big favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.31,0:17:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.54,0:17:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only hope left for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.53,0:17:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, I didn't happen to\Nbe there just by coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.66,0:17:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I went there looking for\Nyou after Layla asked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.18,0:17:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Miss Layla?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.90,0:18:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I've heard the gist of\Nwhat happened at Kaleido Stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.90,0:18:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.56,0:18:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I think this is too tough for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.81,0:18:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.89,0:18:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, you really don't know\Nwhat kind of place this festival is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.91,0:18:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the place that can\Nmake your dreams come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.11,0:18:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But at the same time, it's also a place\Nwhere you destroy the dreams of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.50,0:18:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.95,0:18:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I also know that victory\Nmeans beating everybody else.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.75,0:18:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I have to win here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.21,0:18:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, there's no such thing as\Nfair play, friendship, or consideration.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.76,0:18:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you let your guard down,\Nsomeone will get the jump on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.31,0:18:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know this is that kind of world?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.11,0:18:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.56,0:18:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, for example, if a friend of yours,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.79,0:19:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,let's say Ken,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.58,0:19:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,suddenly collapsed just before you perform,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.71,0:19:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you received a call saying that he\Nwas in the hospital and wanting to see you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.81,0:19:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What would you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.88,0:19:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.72,0:19:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's possible that the call was a\Nlie made up by another performer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.42,0:19:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.80,0:19:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I think that question \Nwas a little mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.36,0:19:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.85,0:19:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.42,0:19:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's participate in the festival together.\NI will submit an entry application tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.18,0:19:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.63,0:19:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is where you live.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.33,0:19:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow... Did you paint all these, Yuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.31,0:19:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.50,0:19:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What with spending all my time commuting\Nback and forth between here and school,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.68,0:19:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,maybe I started wanting some company.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.82,0:19:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just casually picked up a brush,\Nand then I was completely into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.01,0:19:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone is smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.84,0:20:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was at Kaleido Stage,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.24,0:20:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I looked at\Nthe audience's faces much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.59,0:20:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I started painting,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.86,0:20:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I realized how wonderful smiling faces were.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.28,0:20:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the picture you're painting now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.74,0:20:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. When I tried to capture the\Nessence of the smile, it became an angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.81,0:20:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Angel...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.61,0:20:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's May. I'd like to start\Ntraining soon, if that's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.86,0:20:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.78,0:20:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, this is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.33,0:20:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leon Oswald, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.94,0:20:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to beat Leon and May's Demon Spiral,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.06,0:21:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose we need a maneuver on par with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.99,0:21:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we try an angel's maneuver?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.42,0:21:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An angel's maneuver?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.98,0:21:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. To counter \Ntheir demon maneuver.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.89,0:21:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.23,0:21:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.90,0:21:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will help your practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.87,0:21:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mute and Alice?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.83,0:21:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be hard because\Nyou don't have too much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.49,0:21:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we also can learn something if we\Nget to watch the previous winner's practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.84,0:21:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want to do, Sora?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.22,0:21:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since they offered us a hand,\NI think we should accept their offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.48,0:21:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what she says.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.43,0:21:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.51,0:21:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.26,0:21:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even among those\Npeople who enter the festival,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.56,0:21:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}there are nice people like Mute and Alice.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.20,0:21:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good! Then, go higher like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.13,0:21:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Not good at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.12,0:21:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.44,0:21:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it like you're flying\Nupwards on your own power!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.14,0:21:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.32,0:22:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I won't lose to May! I'll definitely win!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.15,0:22:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In order to meet Miss Layla's expectations.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.95,0:22:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Demon Spiral!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.51,0:22:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That speed is your limit?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.36,0:22:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I can go faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.66,0:22:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then speed up to your limit!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.87,0:22:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.27,0:22:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Do it more slowly.\NLike an angel's wings...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.27,0:22:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.65,0:22:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, this is a winning candidate's maneuver...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.30,0:22:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to win no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.81,0:22:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one to win will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.36,0:22:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.23,0:22:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sekasu you ni muragaru Hard luck{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.84,0:22:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nagasarete Time is over {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.97,0:22:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yokoku doori Take it easy {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.68,0:23:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tsuredasu yo imasugu {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.16,0:23:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hurry up (Here we go) {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.85,0:23:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gouin only (saisoku drive) {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.14,0:23:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nichijou miorosu best view {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.54,0:23:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sunset point (Favorite) {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.49,0:23:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Harbor light (Stormy night) {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.37,0:23:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Asu no tame ni escape {\i0}
